com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.entities

Class CommandSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.entities.CommandSettings

  • public class CommandSettings
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides a very basic level of configuration.

    All settings declared through this class can also be declared on a guild specific level. Therefore use the JDACommands.getGuildSettings() method. If no guild settings are present, the default settings will be used instead.

    Since:
    1.0.0
    Version:
